title: 30 Litre Bin Liners 100 Bags, Biodegradable Food Waste Garbage Bags, 30L Strong Compostable Trash Caddy Liners, Recycling Degradable Rubbish Bag for Kitchen Bathroom Garden Office, Green, 60 x 65cm
features: Biodegradable Bin Bags – XOTOZO 30l biodegradable food waste bags are non-toxic and harmless. Our trash bags are made from corn starch, compostable and biodegradable. Ideal compostable caddy liners for a better participation in protecting the environment!

Reliable & Leak Resistant Garbage Bags – With the size of 60cm (W) x 65cm (H), these 30l rubbish bags are ideal for most kitchen/garden bins. A special octagonal design is adopted on the bottom of compostable caddy liners for firm corners and super load-bearing. Extra thickness of bin bags to avoid puncture, leakage and splits.
100 Breakpoint Food Waste Bags – Each package includes 100 trash bags (5 rolls, 20 bags per roll). The breakpoint design ensures easy tearing of these rubbish bags without being ripped.

Multi-Purpose Waste Bags – These 30 Litres bin bags perfectly fit most bins and pedal bins for indoor use. Thick material and large enough size make these compostable bin liners an ideal choice for kitchen, bathroom, living room, bedroom, office and garden use.

Better Environment Protection – Every time you order our XOTOZO 30 Litres Biodegradable Bin Liners, you help reduce the amount of those harmful black plastic bags entering circulation and better protect your surrounding environment.
